re it began to be used also by Christians from the 14th century onwards and especially at the time of the Reformation, when Old Testament names became popular. It was very common among the Puritans in the 17th century, and has enjoyed a tremendous vogue in England since the latter part of the 20th century, among people of many different creeds. In Scotland this is found as an Anglicized form of Beathag ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Rebecca was born in 1210, in Hereford, Herefordshire, England, United Kingdom. She married Randal de Marbury in 1234, in Hereford, Herefordshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1210–":"1210–Surnud","1210–Male":"1210–Surnud","1234–Male":"1234–Surnud","1210–Female":"1210–Surnud","1234":"1234","1210":"1210","Weobley, Herefordshire, England":"Weobley, Herefordshire, England","Hereford, Herefordshire, England":"Hereford, Herefordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1210–":"1210–Kuollut","1210–Male":"1210–Kuollut","1234–Male":"1234–Kuollut","1210–Female":"1210–Kuollut","1234":"1234","1210":"1210","Weobley, Herefordshire, England":"Weobley, Herefordshire, England","Hereford, Herefordshire, England":"Hereford, Herefordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1210–":"1210–Décédée","1210–Male":"1210–Décédé","1234–Male":"1234–Décédé","1210–Female":"1210–Décédée","1234":"1234","1210":"1210","Weobley, Herefordshire, England":"Weobley, Herefordshire, Angleterre","Hereford, Herefordshire, England":"Hereford, Herefordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Rebecca est née en 1210, à Hereford, Herefordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé Randal de Marbury en 1234, à Hereford, Herefordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1210–":"1210–Verstorben","1210–Male":"1210–Verstorben","1234–Male":"1234–Verstorben","1210–Female":"1210–Verstorben","1234":"1234","1210":"1210","Weobley, Herefordshire, England":"Weobley, Herefordshire, England","Hereford, Heref